* New: SQLite3-backed session and progress persistence (--enable-sqlite3-persistence).
* New: aria2.getDownloadResultCount, aria2.searchDownloadResult,
       aria2.exportSession, aria2.requeueDownloadResult RPC methods.
* New: --sqlite3-db-path, --sqlite3-history-limit options.
* New: FEATURE_SQLITE3_PERSISTENCE in --version output and aria2.getVersion.
* Fix: aria2.saveSession RPC writes to all configured session backends
       (was: text only); behavior matches periodic --save-session-interval flush.
